column1: #Text=Tonraq says : " Get the men and fall back . "
#Text=Tonraq says : " I 'm going to end this , right now .
#Text=" Unalaq says : " Brother , I 'm too strong for you .
#Text=" Tonraq says : " You 're no brother of mine .
#Text=You betrayed me , you had me banished !
#Text=" Tonraq says : " You are not the true chief .
